# v0.7.1 — pin SQL files to LF line endings so SHA-256(schema.sql) is
# stable across runners + filesystems. MigrateCommand hashes the file
# byte-exact (DOCS #63); a future Windows checkout would otherwise
# auto-convert LF→CRLF and the hash would mismatch even though the
# semantics didn't change.
*.sql text eol=lf
